name: Types of Fruit
author: Kevin Nieskes
content: Apples, pears, grape, another grape, blue grape, blue rasberry, lemon lime, and Mt. Dew. Scientists speculate that as many as 4 other fruits may exist. Unconfirmed reports claim that a fruit called snozberries has been discovered though no reports can confirm it.

name: New Fruit discovered!
author: Kevin Nieskes
content: Scientists have just annouced a new exotic fruit called... oranges. Monsanto's latest product tastes just like Sunny D!

name: Are there more than 7 Fruits?
author: Kevin Nieskes
content: Some people have told me there are hundreds of fruits. This is not true.

name: New discovery!
author: Kevin Nieskes
content: Did you guys know about apples? There pretty cool. I just read about them in the newspaper. Apparently they are a red egg.

name: Log entry #94445841
author: Kevin Nieskes
content: There all around me now. I won't last much longer. If I die, tell my wife, hello.
